      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The sale of an irrigated acre\ntract that is alleged to have lacked\nthe irrigation was the occasion for\na suit for $4,000 damages filed today\nby c. II. Pierce and wife against\nthe American Securities Co.\n\n\nPierce said that he was guaran-\nteed water when he bought the\nacre tract in Jameson Park at $500\nper acre. He claims that he put In\nwhole seasons hard work and\nthat his wife ruined her health car\nrying water, which failed to be de-\nlivered on the contract as agreed\nupon."
